hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-休班sir : 唔該你躝屍趌路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-創新大師（潮語先驅）： 自由閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-上水天橋肥屍 ： 見敵人就捉，追到天荒地老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-所有警察代表 ： 統人自己勢力，唔理好醜「放」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14520886c62b93885e0a06625fe185ee093ea216","tid":1313792,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9843a2f253ba4af2233997d15d506ba2fd6f45e3","tid":1313792,"uid":268540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:24:45.000Z","msg":"估唔到我都有fans"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:39:59.000Z","msg":"有冇幸可以升級為死忠<br />\n你好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你做得好好，我以為睇古惑仔真人版<br />\n特別係嗰條發際線，J撚到我出血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0baf37eee25c4dfd5c51a6ea28742677dc46c504","tid":1313792,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2b68e8582296860f57e5d2e7d374bb2cb76f1a6","tid":1313792,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:18:33.000Z","msg":"Cosplay要去到連行為行動神似<br />\n記住要學足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW<br />\n勇既做野顧唔到四周<br />\n和理既要適當時候制止去救人<br />\n唔好阻人，阻人同令勇者冇仇報<br />\nCosplay放人冇分別<br />\n記住係救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:42:35.000Z","msg":"記住要雙管齊下，各有各做<br />\n承擔到就去<br />\n包袱大就做掩護"},{"pid":"d5463e49212f50e6a62c4e365fb3987d8b8e8a31","tid":1313792,"uid":268540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14520886c62b93885e0a06625fe185ee093ea216","tid":1313792,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9843a2f253ba4af2233997d15d506ba2fd6f45e3","tid":1313792,"uid":268540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-